title: ‘Atlanta’ Episode 15, ‘Dubai’ Finale, and ‘Southern Charm’ Episode 10
description:
This week on 'Morally Corrupt,' Rachel is joined by Chelsea Stark-Jones to discuss the ‘Beverly Hills’ related Bravo news of the week (2:39). Then they move on to recap ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta’ Season 14, Episode 15 (18:59), rate and review ’The Real Housewives of Dubai’ Season 1 finale (33:55), and break down ‘Southern Charm’ Season 8, Episode 10 (62:57).
Host: Rachel Lindsay
Guests: Chelsea Stark-Jones
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
Theme Song: Devon Renaldo
